<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="iddce2f2b5-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1996-01-01">Jan. 1, 1996</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/104/65/s24">section 24 of Pub. L. 104–65</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t2/s1601">section 1601 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
